我写个代码给你用用新建一个类，类名随你，我这里叫做MoreFuelHandler
public class MoreFuelHandler
  implements IFuelHandler
{
  public int getBurnTime(ItemStack fuel)
  {
    Item burnItem = fuel.getItem();
    if (((burnItem instanceof ItemBlock)) && (Block.getBlockFromItem(burnItem) != Blocks.air))
    {
      Block block = Block.getBlockFromItem(burnItem);

      if (block == Blocks.stone) return 200;//让石头和草能作为燃料，燃料值为200，可以自己变通成自己的方块
      if (block == Blocks.glass) return 200;
      return 0;
    }

    if (burnItem == Items.book) return 200;//让书和苹果能作为燃料，燃烧值为200
    if (burnItem == Items.apple) return 200;
    return 0;
  }复制代码别忘了在主类注册这个类哦
GameRegistry.registerFuelHandler(new MoreFuelHandler());
